sub_title: Owner of USA Car Import, wholesale, vehicle sourcing, in- export of USA vehicles world-wide.
summary:
Founded in 2007, USA CAR IMPORT is a wholesale automotive company specialized in vehicle sourcing and world-wide distribution of new and pre-owned quality vehicles from North America US, Canada & Mexico. Wholesale & fleet pricing for most American vehicles: passenger cars , pick-ups, luxury & exotic cars, limousines, armored cars, hearses, ambulances, recreational vehicles and trucks. World-wide clients are (brand-)dealers, (leasing-) companies and private persons.

USA Car Import : Depuis 2007, nous sommes un grossiste et importateur spécialisé dans les voitures neuves et faible kilométrage. Nous avons des clients en Europe et mondial, et des bureaux à Amsterdam, Caen, France et en Floride.
